item.title: Delta server help please!
item.dc:creator: @RandQm RandQm
item.description:
@RandQm wrote:

Try changing everything to 127.0.0.1 both server and client sided.
And don’t forget to compile both server and client.

If this works then u can re add no-ip details.
Don’t forget to compile!
